title: Gold Coast light rail gets $95m federal funding boost in time for 2018 Commonwealth Games
text: The Federal Government commits $95 million for the proposed expansion of the Gold Coast Light Rail project, with Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull saying it is a vital piece of infrastructure for Queensland. ...
